  ## What is OptaPlanner?

  **OptaPlanner optimizes business resource usage.** Every organization faces planning problems: provide products or
  services with a limited set of *constrained* resources (employees, assets, time and money). OptaPlanner optimizes such
  planning to do more business with less resources.

  OptaPlanner is a lightweight, embeddable planning engine written in Java™. It helps normal Java™ programmers solve
  constraint satisfaction problems efficiently. Under the hood, it combines optimization heuristics and metaheuristics
  with very efficient score calculation.

  *OptaPlanner is open source software, released under [the Apache Software License](code/license.html). It is 100% pure
  Java™, runs on any JVM and is available in [the Maven Central Repository](download/download.html) too.*

